  <brief_title>Comparison of Lipophilic Versus Hydrophilic Statins on Patients With Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of Lipophilic Versus Hydrophilic Statin Administration on The Clinical Outcome and Cardiac Markers of Patients With Heart Failure</official_title>
